oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Report on improved use of research facilities and topics relevant for integration, and training schemes
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: Nykänen, Arja
oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: "Organics" in general
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: This report describes the possibilities of different research facilities to fulfil the research needs established by the participating countries of the CORE Organic project. The report is based on information given in the WP4 report, WP6 report and WP6 final report.
oai_dc:dc.dc:identifier: Nykänen, Arja (2007) Report on improved use of research facilities and topics relevant for integration, and training schemes. CORE Organic.
